data.title: Exquisite Senior Living in North Quincy, MA
data.meta_description: Atria Marina Place is an exquisite senior community 10 minutes from Boston in North Quincy, MA, offering an active lifestyle and abundant amenities. Tour today.
data.text:
Exquisite Senior Living, Assisted Living and Memory Care in North Quincy

Atria Marina Place is located inside the seaside enclave of Marina Bay in North Quincy, just 10 minutes from Boston. Feel the cool breeze from the water as you enjoy your ideal senior lifestyle close to beaches.

Starting at $4,795 / month

See Pricing & Floor Plans

This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply.

Explore the neighborhood

Fun things to do inside your community are just the beginning. Take in the views at Squantum Point Park and fish on the pier, or go for a stroll with friends along Wollaston Beach. Looking for another way to get your steps in? Hit the links at Boston Golf and Social before meeting friends for a pie from Puritan Pizza. Celebrate with a special dinner at Venezia Restaurant Boston or enjoy waterfront views at Siros Restaurant. Discover an active senior lifestyle at Atria Marina Place, an assisted living and memory care community.
